data.description: Discover this exceptional property in an ideal location. Nestled in the tranquil bluffs on the western edge of Pueblo West, this home offers views that will take your breath away. The upper-level living room is a highlight, featuring expansive windows that flood the space with natural light and provide the perfect vantage point to savor the stunning vistas. The kitchen, complete with an eat-in area, offers a convenient exit to the raised rear deck, making it the ideal spot to relish a morning coffee or an evening sunset. Down the hall, you'll find two bedrooms and a full bathroom, providing comfortable living quarters. The lower level boasts a family room with a wood-burning stove for cozy gatherings, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. Here, you'll also discover two additional bedrooms and a 3/4 bathroom, ensuring space for family, guests, or versatility in use. Throughout the house, you'll find durable LVP flooring and newer carpet, enhancing the overall appeal and comfort of the home. For your parking and storage needs, a two-car detached garage and ample parking space are available, providing room for your vehicles and more. All of this is set on a generous 1.28-acre parcel, ensuring space, privacy, and endless possibilities.  Radon system already in place! This is an incredible opportunity to own a property that combines a great home with a breathtaking location. Don't miss the chance to experience it for yourself – schedule your viewing today!
